  <h1>Leaves, Pages, Bites, & Bytes!</h1>
   <p style="color:purple;">

      Welcome to the Xanadu_Cafe & Nook! It is a cyber-bookstore-nature cafe maintained through sustainable management and policies to ensure the peace for
      digital users, book lovers, those who prefer a cup of coffee and a piece of yummy cake as a getaway from urban lifestyles as well as stressful 
      pressures from schools and/or work.
</p>
  
 
  <img src="Logo design for 'Xanadu_Cafe  Nook', a serene, eco-conscious cyber cafÃ© and bookstore. The logo sho.jpeg" alt="Xanadu_Cafe & Nook Logo" width="400">
   
   <h2 style="color:lightskyblue;">Our Offerings</h2>
   <ul>
   <li>Lounges for coffee, reading, and chats with other people</li>
   <li>Bookstores by walls for literary authenticity in the digital world</li>
   <li>Artificial trees with WiFi routers for internet connectivity</li>
   <li>Real trees for air circulation and nourishing smells of nature</li>
   <li>Private computers for people with no technological resources</li>
   <li>Eco-friendly packaging for food and drinks and compositing bins for leftovers for local agricultural practices</li>
   </ul>
   


   <section>
   <h2 style="color:lightskyblue;">Menu - Food</h2>

